Update meson.build

bump webp dependency to avoid builds against a vulerable libwebp version

io-webp.c: Use incremental loading and do not allocate resources on get_info
tests/t_icc.c: fix formatting
tests: add test to feed jpeg data
icc: read ICCP chunk from WebP file and encode as base64 in the read GdkPixbuf's "icc-profile" option
tests: add missing t_scaled.c
